Summary
-----------------------------------------------------------------------

DBMapper has no npm dependencies and no bundled assets. The only
third-party code loaded at runtime is:

  - Materialize 1.0.0 (MIT)
  - Inter (SIL OFL 1.1)
  - JetBrains Mono (SIL OFL 1.1)
  - Material Icons (Apache 2.0)

The SQL parser (`parseSQLToTables` in `app.js`) is self-contained and does
not call into any third-party library.

Tests run on Node.js and use only the `node:assert` and `node:fs` built-ins;
no test-side third-party packages are required.
